Heat oven to 350 degrees F. In large bowl, combine salsa, chili, mushrooms. Parmesan cheese and Italian seasoning. In small bowl, combine cottage cheese and parsley flakes. In 9-inch baking dish coated with cooking spray, layer 3 noodles, 1/2 cup cottage cheese, 1/3 of chili mixture and 1/3 of the mozzarella cheese. Repeat to make 3 layers. Bake 25 to 30 minutes or until cheese is melted and bubbly. Let stand 10 minutes before serving.